    "description": "This set aims to hit as hard and fast as possible with Choice Scarf and Outrage, which dents everything that doesn't resist it. Unfortunately, being locked into a Dragon-type move leaves it vulnerable to Fairy-types, which completely wall Deino. Even with Hustle and a decent Attack stat, Deino still struggles to break past certain defensive Pokemon. Its reliance on Choice Scarf to be effective further hurts its ability to find a spot on a team. Overall, this set is outclassed by other wallbreakers like Rufflet, which also has Hustle and arguably better coverage, and Cranidos, which has a far superior Attack stat. There are also better choices for Choice Scarf users, such as Snivy.",
