    "setName": "[BW] Choice Scarf",
    "description": "Gastly carves a niche for itself as a revenge killer thanks to its solid Special Attack and immunities to Normal, Fighting, and Ground; these immunities, particularly the immunity to Persian's Fake Out, distinguish Gastly from more common Choice Scarf users like Simisear, Mr. Mime, and Grumpig. STAB Shadow Ball has great neutral coverage and hits staple offensive Pokemon like Grumpig, Mr. Mime, and Solrock very hard. Sludge Bomb grants a slightly stronger STAB move with decent neutral coverage against Normal-types and the occasional Vullaby while offering a very valuable super effective hit on the Grass-types, Meganium and Leafeon. Hidden Power Ground is critical coverage for Gastly to revenge kill Rock Polish Lairon, but it has few other uses than catching Lairon and Pawniard trying to switch in. Trick is Gastly's best method of disrupting walls like Clefairy, Wormadam-S, and Munchlax, and it allows Gastly to freely switch moves against slower teams.\nChoice Scarf Gastly is a good fit for offensive teams in need of a strong form of speed control that compresses several immunities. Muk is a huge issue for Gastly between its high special bulk and Shadow Sneak OHKOing Gastly, so Solrock is a great partner for Gastly. Arbok makes a great partner to Gastly by checking Muk, and in turn, Gastly is often untouchable for passive walls like Hippopotas and Vibrava that would trouble Arbok. Walrein and Whiscash can use Clefairy and Wormadam-S as setup fodder, so they appreciate Gastly luring them in while benefitting from the strong speed control Gastly offers, particularly against Leafeon. Partners like Muk and Mienfoo can cover Gastly's rough matchup against Clefairy while also absorbing special and physical hits, respectively. Raichu is a solid partner for Gastly that is capable of breaking Clefairy while benefitting from from Gastly threatening Meganium, which is often difficult for Raichu to break on its own, and faster attackers like Persian and Choice Scarf Mienfoo.",
