    "setName": "[BW] Physical Sweeper",
    "description": "This set makes the best use of what Swinub has to offer. Earthquake gets\nSTAB, and Swinub can spam it thanks to its great coverage and high base\npower. Superpower is amazing coverage to hit Ferroseed and is a good\noption over Icicle Spear now that it became legal. Icicle Spear is still\na good powerful STAB to be using when facing Subs or just getting more\npower on attacks than with Ice Shard. Icicle Shard is great for picking\noff sweepers and any faster Pokemon that survives one of Swinub's first\nmoves. Stealth Rock is on the set as Swinub can set it up easily, since\nSwinub causes many switches. Using Life Orb ties up the set by boosting\nSwinub's offensive prowess to sky high levels.\nSnow Cloak is the preferred ability when using Swinub. As such, Snover\npairs well with Swinub, as Swinub's Grass-type weakness is covered by\nSnover. Snover brings out the permanent hail that will kick Swinub's\nability into use. Jolly is generally the preferred nature for the extra\nspeed to speed tie with the common benchmark of 15 Speed, although\nAdamant is a suitable alternative considering Swinub's low Attack. Rock\nSlide can be used as a filler move, but it won't see much use otherwise.\nIcicle Crash can be used over Icicle Spear for more consistent damage,\nalthough low accuracy and inability to break Substitutes aren't helpful.",
